    <briefdescription>
<para>System-level port interface — functions the user must implement. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides critical-section management, a millisecond tick source, delay, and system reset. These are required by several SyntropicOS modules. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
